as innocent people tend to do,

34:37.045 --> 34:39.268
and volunteered the information.

34:39.268 --> 34:41.655
And the only reason they arrested him,

34:41.655 --> 34:46.165
was because of a video and an opinion
proferred by an eccentric therapist

34:46.165 --> 34:50.873
who runs around telling people
