34:50.873 --> 34:54.648
This case can't turn on his credibility.

34:54.648 --> 34:56.838
Talk about reasonable doubt.

34:56.838 --> 34:58.434
Reasonable doubt.

34:58.434 --> 35:00.573
Come on, it could have been him,

35:00.573 --> 35:02.327
