“reasonable doubt,”

35:09.789 --> 35:16.191
which is typically the case
when the police don't investigate.

35:42.339 --> 35:44.076
Oh, my God.

35:44.319 --> 35:46.226
That was amazing.

35:50.466 --> 35:55.088
